spellgem5  [random spell  spellgem6  [random spell name]<br />
spellgem7  [random spell  spellgem8  [random spell name]<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Something like that. See how the first set of &quot;random spell names&quot;  get cut off? What I am trying to do is like this -<br />
<br />
