<br />
<br />
Can anyone help me do this? Again, I'm trying to get this to work with the Quartz skin. :) I'd even be willing to try taking the spell bar out of that area completely, moving it to a different place, then replacing the blank spot that would be there with some sort of texture that is similar to the Quartz skin.<br />
